{"tid":621510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有隻蝗嬸係地鐵逃票","createTime":"2018-04-08T11:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:33:16.000Z","uid":31209,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9f830e4b6852de468a11eb39a1b51829aee0f1","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"係迪士尼站入閘時見到有個女人係閘口行嚟行去唔知做乜鳩<br />\n當我入閘後望轉頭見到個女人跟貼個女仔入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個女仔走去同黃衫人報串話有隻蝗無買飛入閘<br />\n我就幫手指證邊隻蝗嬸逃票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n職員話罰翻隻蝗車錢<br />\n抵撚你死啊有錢去迪士尼玩冇錢比嗰幾蚊坐車<br />\n寒酸到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween平時用學生飛，地鐵就捉到你罰錢<br />\n今次罰得隻蝗比車錢都算輕手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗蟲快啲死撚哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de24f14529313e51f88ebcdd016c064d5817f2b1","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f67742bb46bcc5d0258ddd91097c21d07c5a4f","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n趕絕蝗蟲你我有責"},{"pid":"c7a79720970399bb68255463b226d0bf341cf3ee","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42563c4c003a77b489260f75f00e38be1a48065f","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:17:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6908ec36dbcae95fa7a37b4123be96275bc14b8","tid":