id":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"仲好記得細個大約初中時跟屋企人去中國旅行<br />\n要排隊坐車落山，啲蝗一見到車就衝撚哂去上車<br />\n明明成條隊係到，而下個就係我同屋企人上車<br />\n之後老豆同佢啲朋友就鬧鳩啲蝗打尖<br />\n點知比啲蝗鬧翻轉頭話請用文明的方式溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母邊撚個唔文明啊而家<br />\n應該由嗰陣就植根對蝗嘅憎恨同歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到而家我仲好記住呢班人冇文明可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00e898c8817b8ad3e64a73aecf68bb4b2a42208","tid":621510,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"劣根性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b3492e7af004b624569aa41bc637a918a8aaff","tid":621510,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"補回車費有撚用咩"}]}